
1. JS
 - load scripts from node_modules
 - load custom scripts from resource folder
 - have custom scripts for each page like index.js, products.js, etc.
 - load modules with requirejs or browserifyjs in these custom scripts
 - end point js to be minified if env is production
 - custom js outside node_modules to go through jshint/jslint
 - generate sourcemaps

2. CSS
 - compile custom sass
 - concat custom css
 - load css from node_modules
 - end point css to be minified if env is production
 - make sourcemaps
 - output errors in console